ent. If the star formation occurred both in the collapsed core and the\naccreted envelope, then the resultant star cluster has a double main sequence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2010 08:46:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-24"}
